metadata.name: Happy Accidents
metadata.description:
Looking to add a little bit of art into your life? Check out this one-of-a-kind Bob Ross sphynx cat NFT! 

This hilarious photograph features Norman, the hairless sphynx cat, dressed up in a wig and costume made to look like the iconic painter. Whether you're a fan of Bob Ross or just love cats, you won't want to miss out on this unique piece of digital art. We don't make meowstakes, just happy accidents! 

Photographed by award-winning cat photographer, Brooke Arnold.
